希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 向去世的《巅峰黑帮》服装设计师斯蒂芬妮·科利 (Stephanie Collie) 致敬https://www.nme.com/news/tv/cillian-murphy-leads-tributes-to-peaky-blinders-costume-designer-stephanie-collie-who-has-died-3814498?utm _source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=cillian-murphy-leads-向peaky-blinders-costume-designer-stephanie-collie-who-has-died致敬Elizabeth AubreyWed, 20 Nov 2024 19:43:29 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV News.. https://www.nme.com/?p=3814498 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="希里安·墨菲" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “斯蒂芬妮是一位才华横溢的人。她发明了‘Peaky Blinders’造型”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/cillian-murphy-leads-tributes-to-peaky-blinders-costume-designer-stephanie-collie-who-has-died-3814498">希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 的帖子向《巅峰黑帮》的服装设计师斯蒂芬妮·科利 (Stephanie Collie) 表示敬意，她去世后</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="希里安·墨菲" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cillian-Murphy-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Lionsgate-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cillian-murphy">希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy)</a>向 60 岁去世的<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/peaky-blinders"><i>《浴血黑帮》</i></a>服装设计师斯蒂芬妮·柯莉 (Stephanie Collie) 致敬。</p><p>许多其他演员也向这位演员致敬，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-reynolds">瑞安·雷诺兹</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daniel-craig">丹尼尔·克雷格</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/samuel-l-jackson">塞缪尔·杰克逊</a>，他们都曾与这位著名的服装设计师合作过。</p><p>这一消息通过英国广播公司<i>《浴血黑帮</i>》官方 Instagram 账户与粉丝们分享，并向 Collie 的“鼓舞人心”的工作表示敬意。</p><p>声明中写道：“得知服装设计师斯蒂芬妮·科利去世的消息，我们感到非常悲伤。</p><p> “斯蒂芬妮在我们的第一个系列中所做的令人难以置信的工作是创造<i>《浴血黑帮》</i>标志性外观的关键，并继续激励着世界各地的许多人。</p><p> “我们的爱和思念与她的家人同在。”</p><p>墨菲在剧中扮演汤米·谢尔比<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/tommy-shelby-returns-in-peaky-blinders-movie-first-look-image-3798419#:~:text=Production%20has%20begun%20on%20Netflix,Cillian%20Murphy%20as%20Tommy%20Shelby.&amp;text=The%20film%20was%20first%20confirmed,Tom%20Harper%20set%20to%20direct.">，目前正在拍摄新的衍生电影</a>，他分享了他对柯利犬的深情致敬。</p><p>他在一份声明中写道：“斯蒂芬妮是一位才华横溢的人。她发明的<i>《浴血黑帮》的</i>外观和轮廓已成为全世界的标志。</p><p> “我们都会想念她的。安息吧。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCjlnvHs0qX/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.106,7